{"tid":1349318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟日報集團發表聲明 石鏡泉言論純屬個人意見","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T13:46:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52a8bddad3a80d28f0a8af3b9e942fadb5ae29b5","tid":1349318,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"經濟日報集團一向支持社會透過以和平、理性及非暴力去表達訴求。理解近期社會上出現不同聲音及對前景的憂慮，希望事件能儘快平息。本報反對並嚴厲譴責任何暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n經濟日報副社長石鏡泉強調，日前以<span style=\"color: red;\">私人身份出席一個公開活動，其所發表言論，純屬個人意見</span>。石鏡泉同時為經濟日報集團旗下刊物長期作者，一如其他作者，集團尊重其言論自由。<br />\n <br />\n經濟日報集團旗下刊物編採守則一向秉持「三公一中」，公平、公道、公正及中肯，尤其是這個紛擾時代，由前綫記者採訪、攝影、後勤製圖、標題到把關編輯等等，在處理新聞、分析和評論上更嚴格以事實為基礎。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2407477/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2407477%2F&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKkqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=1bee68fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2407477/</a>"},{"pid":"1cd551e299c70421ce9654459f5ba0f519581d7a","tid":1349318,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2bf68df7702f1bf894027e0caa13fa474bb14a","tid":1349318,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"5a7f889a0255cb44e77326000dffbf37c80e130e","tid":1349318,"uid":174084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:07:44.000Z","msg":"打殺所有同石鏡泉有關一切刊物"},{"pid":"f65250784605e9bd02c4d54823fa99b47fed42a9","tid":1349318,"uid":229289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"U magazine 8"},{"pid":"31c5e682d825b53f8c73c0b275a8c4c77723be03","tid":1349318,"uid":41246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:46:49.000Z","msg":"damage is done<br />\n而家講乜都冇用，等收皮啦"}]}